603
00:28:18,559 --> 00:28:20,040
Quanquan!

604
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:23,720
I'm such a bad mummy.

605
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:25,200
Let me down.

606
00:28:26,040 --> 00:28:27,319
