713
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:30,359
Thank you, Quanquan.

714
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:31,680
Enough.

715
00:33:31,920 --> 00:33:32,559
Quanquan.

716
00:33:32,839 --> 00:33:33,639
