724
00:33:55,040 --> 00:33:56,599
It looks like you.

725
00:34:00,399 --> 00:34:01,520
This is for me.

726
00:34:05,520 --> 00:34:06,639
Quanquan.

727
00:34:08,079 --> 00:34:08,719
Quanquan.

728
00:34:08,719 --> 00:34:10,159
My gift is way better.

729
00:34:24,639 --> 00:34:25,400
Zizhu.

730
