736
00:34:35,599 --> 00:34:36,400
I don't know.

737
00:34:36,759 --> 00:34:37,559
Love for all.

738
00:34:37,759 --> 00:34:39,279
They suit you quite well.

739
00:34:40,199 --> 00:34:41,279
I didn't know.

740
00:34:41,279 --> 00:34:42,159
How about you tell me

741
